                <img src="/assets/img/sustainability/icons/products--green.png" alt="icon product green" class="offerings__header__img">
                <h1 class="offerings__heading">
                    SUSTAINABLE OFFERINGS
                </h1>
                <small class="offerings__small">Sage carefully sources several types of yarn that enhance the ability to create sustainable fabrics<br> based on the needs of each OEM. Experience our sustainable&nbsp;solutions:</small>
                <div class="offerings__grid">
                    <div class="offerings__item">
                        <img class="offerings__img" src="/assets/img/sustainability/icons/post-consumer-yarns.png" alt="bottle">
                        <div class="offerings__item-txt">
                            <h2 class="offerings__h2">POST-CONSUMER YARNS</h2>
                            <small class="offerings__small">made from recycled bottles</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="offerings__item">
                        <img class="offerings__img" src="/assets/img/sustainability/icons/biobased.png" alt="biobased yarn">
                        <div class="offerings__item-txt">
                            <h2 class="offerings__h2">BIOBASED YARNS</h2>
                            <small class="offerings__small">partially made out of renewable, natural rawmaterials - 30% biobased resource (MEG) + 70% fossil based (PTA)</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="offerings__item">
                        <img class="offerings__img" src="/assets/img/sustainability/icons/post-industrial-yarns.png" alt="post-industrial recycle">
                        <div class="offerings__item-txt">
                            <h2 class="offerings__h2">POST-INDUSTRIAL YARNS</h2>
                            <small class="offerings__small">made from many sources of industrial polyester that have not been sold to the end&nbsp;consumer</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="offerings__item">
                        <img class="offerings__img" src="/assets/img/sustainability/icons/wool.png" alt="wool">
                        <div class="offerings__item-txt">
                            <h2 class="offerings__h2">WOOL</h2>
                            <small class="offerings__small">high-quality eco-fabric that is thermo-regulated and anti-static.</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="offerings__item">
                        <img class="offerings__img" src="/assets/img/sustainability/icons/ocean-clean.png" alt="turtle">
                        <div class="offerings__item-txt">
                            <h2 class="offerings__h2">OCEAN-CLEAN YARNS</h2>
                            <small class="offerings__small">protect our waterways and oceans by preventing and removing plastics. There are two ways this is&nbsp;achieved:
                                <br>1) removing: plastic bottles from our&nbsp;oceans<br>2) preventing: ocean-bound plastic&nbsp;bottles</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="offerings__item">
                        <img class="offerings__img" src="/assets/img/sustainability/icons/regen-wool.png" alt="wool">
                        <div class="offerings__item-txt">
                            <h2 class="offerings__h2">REGENERATED WOOL</h2>
                            <small class="offerings__small">upcycles waste that’s either destined for a landfill or generated during production.</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="offerings__item">
                        <img class="offerings__img" src="/assets/img/sustainability/icons/fabric-complex.png" alt="fabric">
                        <div class="offerings__item-txt">
                            <h2 class="offerings__h2">NON-WOVEN LAMINATION</h2>
                            <small class="offerings__small">offers a higher loft and good cushioning properties and adds sustainable value by using a fleece lamination.</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="offerings__item less-margin">
                        <img class="offerings__img" src="/assets/img/sustainability/icons/alpaca.png" alt="wool">
                        <div class="offerings__item-txt">
                            <h2 class="offerings__h2">ALPACA</h2>
                            <small class="offerings__small">only created in natural color/shades, which saves water and energy consumption.</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="offerings__item">
                        <img class="offerings__img" src="/assets/img/sustainability/icons/tape-weaving.png" alt="woven material">
                        <div class="offerings__item-txt">
                            <h2 class="offerings__h2">TAPE WEAVING</h2>
                            <small class="offerings__small">utilizes innovative tape materials, woven or knit, to create a handcrafted look; recycled materials&nbsp;can&nbsp;be&nbsp;used</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="offerings__item less-margin">
                        <img class="offerings__img" src="/assets/img/sustainability/icons/3d-fabric.png" alt="woven material">
                        <div class="offerings__item-txt">
                            <h2 class="offerings__h2">MONOMATERIAL 3D FABRIC</h2>
                            <small class="offerings__small">100% PES three-dimensional knit that connects front and back knitted fabrics with springy threads.</small>
                        </div>
