    <section class="efforts">
        <div class="content">
            <div class="efforts__heading">
                <img class="efforts__icon" src="/assets/img/sustainability/icons/process--green.png" alt="Process icon">
                <h1 class="efforts__h1">sustainability: the standard<br>at every plant,&nbsp;Everyday</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="efforts-container">
                <div class="efforts__column efforts__description">
                    Sage's overall efforts toward minimizing our environmental footprint are made evident by efforts activities in each of our&nbsp;global&nbsp;locations. <br>Sage Automotive Interior's plants&nbsp;always:                </div>
                <div class="efforts__column efforts__list1">
                    <h2 class="efforts__h2">
                        <img class="efforts-icon" src="/assets/img/sustainability/icons/energy-icon.png" alt="Energy Icon">
                        USE ENERGY EFFICIENTLY TO CONSERVE NATURAL RESOURCES</h2>
                    <h2 class="efforts__h2">
                        <img class="efforts-icon" src="/assets/img/sustainability/icons/reach--recycle.png" alt="Recycle Icon">
                        CONSERVE NATURAL RESOURCES BY REDUCING, RESUING AND RECYCLING MATERIALS</h2>
                    <h2 class="efforts__h2">
                        <img class="efforts-icon" src="/assets/img/sustainability/icons/water-icon.png" alt="Water Icon">
                        UTILIZE SMART, INNOVATIVE WATER MANAGEMENT AND CONSERVATION</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="efforts__column efforts__list2">
                    <h2 class="efforts__h2" style="padding-left: 46px;">
                        <img class="efforts-icon" src="/assets/img/sustainability/icons/cloud-icon.png" style="height:28px !important;" alt="Cloud Icon">
                        MINIMIZE EMISSIONS THAT CONTRIBUTE TO CLIMATE CHANGE</h2>
